{"tid":927631,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【市值蒸發18億】蕭定一旗下HMV數碼中國 股價瀉八成半","createTime":"2018-12-04T09:44:12.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-05T07:44:15.000Z","uid":54373,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"903989a0a9964a6c892e08ca51ff73571c8f53e6","tid":927631,"uid":54373,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-04T09:44:12.000Z","msg":"【更新股價、內容】<br />\nHMV數碼中國（8078）主席蕭定一，名下位於中環及銅鑼灣的唱片店HMV，被指拖欠租金，遭新世界（017）、港鐵（66）追討近500萬元欠租及賠償。有報道指蕭定一正尋求投資者入股打救，惟成事機會不大，HMV或面臨全線結業。<br />\n<br />\nHMV數碼今股價一度低見0.018元，收報0.020元，跌86.93%，市值蒸發18億元，以蕭定一持有8.27%股份計，蕭日內帳面蝕約1.5億。HMVOD視頻（8103）亦挫22.88%，報1.18元。<br />\n<br />\n公司負責人接受傳媒查詢時表示，集團近年多次在業績報告提及零售業務經營困難，並正聯絡新投資者接手HMV零售業務。<br />\n<br />\nHMV 2013年時亦曾告急，當時私募基金匯友資本行政總裁胡景邵以「白武士」身份入主，股份其後悉數賣畀予蕭定一旗下的「中國3D數碼」（即現時的HMV數碼中國），換取其約23%股權。<br />\n<br />\n蕭定一本人2016年一擲1.5億元豪氣購入西半山豪宅殷然頂層複式「天池屋」，過去兩年來，先後四度承按，令半山豪宅淪為提款機。<br />\n<br />\n零售難做，料HMV未來將重心全力轉移至網上業務。"},{"pid":"1ef3976ba0c0f4c777ef5a5134f5de0dd5f22ac7","tid":927631,"uid":133528,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-12-04T09:44:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://encrypted-tbn0.gstatic.com/images?q=tbn:ANd9GcRB3S5K_aP-sG_ucTQG0PiDfCEQYRS8F98OuxR2OIxGwXu3pWY1kA\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fencrypted-tbn0.gstatic.com%2Fimages%3Fq%3Dtbn%3AANd9GcRB3S5K_aP-sG_ucTQG0PiDfCEQYRS8F98OuxR2OIxGwXu3pWY1kA&h=fe4cf341&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"a70b41acdaaf7fcc8df29585f8947fe1e910f0da","tid":927631,"uid":54373,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-04T09:45:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20140604/large/04ec2p7r.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20140604%2Flarge%2F04ec2p7r.jpg&h=db443e84&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"f11800a27770f8b0995b183aebc4e5db86edc3a6","tid":927631,"uid":55257,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1ef3976ba0c0f4c777ef5a5134f5de0dd5